<b>A free press for a fairer world
</b><br><br>

Our collective future is being rapidly reshaped by political, technological=
 and corporate forces focused on the accumulation of power and money. Under=
standing this requires a truly global perspective: this is no time to turn =
inwards.

<br><br>Independent journalism protects democracy internationally and helps=
 protect the truth. Will you choose to support it today?


